phase2.explanation:
You're trying to use an Animator that was never assigned.

**The fix:**
```csharp
void Start()
{
    animator = GetComponent<Animator>();
}

void Update()
{
    if (animator != null)
    {
        animator.SetFloat("Speed", 1f);
    }
}
```

**Sharp-chan says:**
"Always get the Animator component before using it."
